item.title: CVE-2015-10001|2024-08-06T08:58:24.557Z -- unknown -- wp-stats
item.description: The WP-Stats WordPress plugin before 2.52 does not have CSRF check when saving its settings, and did not escape some of them when outputting them, allowing attacker to make logged in high privilege users change them and set Cross-Site Scripting payloads
